<p><img class="right" src="/images/2015-03-15-post-tristans-makerfaire-ideas/IMG_3572.JPG" width="320" height="240">
<img class="left" src="/images/2015-03-15-post-tristans-makerfaire-ideas/IMG_3573.JPG" width="320" height="240">
Here is a picture of a shield that I made at Academy Duello. It was made from wood, with leather for the handle and it was painted with watercolour paints.</p>
